{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-2-chapter-level-2-tsx","path":"/topics/herpes-simplex-ocular/how-this-topic-was-developed/declarations-of-interest/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"eff49877-7550-5fcc-9b16-c54646acfd76","slug":"declarations-of-interest","fullItemName":"Declarations of interest","depth":2,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field b8db9ba6-29c5-4b0a-a6ec-a7f300169dbd --><h2>Declarations of interest</h2><!-- end field b8db9ba6-29c5-4b0a-a6ec-a7f300169dbd -->","summary":null,"htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item aa213e69-0226-4d0e-a9a5-a7f30015bd73 --><!-- begin field b69d5f67-e47c-4e9c-88f3-a7f300169dbd --><h2>Our policy</h2><!-- end field b69d5f67-e47c-4e9c-88f3-a7f300169dbd --><!-- begin field b2e575d9-818a-425b-a7f0-a7f300169dbd --><p>Clarity Informatics requests that all those involved in the writing and reviewing of topics, and those involved in the external review process to declare any competing interests. Signed copies are securely held by Clarity Informatics and are available on request with the permission of the individual. A copy of the declaration of interest form which participants are asked to complete annually is also available on request. A brief outline of the declarations of interest policy is described here and full details of the policy is available on the <a href=\"https://cks.clarity.co.uk/\" data-hyperlink-id=\"cd388483-e530-4037-a608-a992003cfa4c\">Clarity Informatics website</a>. Declarations of interests of the authors are not routinely published, however competing interests of all those involved in the topic update or development are listed below. Competing interests include:</p><ul><li>Personal financial interests</li><li>Personal family interest</li><li>Personal non-financial interest</li><li>Non-personal financial gain or benefit</li></ul><p>Although particular attention is given to interests that could result in financial gains or losses for the individual, competing interests may also arise from academic competition or for political, personal, religious, and reputational reasons. An individual is not obliged to seek out knowledge of work done for, or on behalf of, the healthcare industry within the departments for which they are responsible if they would not normally expect to be informed.</p><!-- end field b2e575d9-818a-425b-a7f0-a7f300169dbd --><!-- begin field 258701da-7ce6-4328-a4c7-a7f300169dbd --><h2>Who should declare competing interests?</h2><!-- end field 258701da-7ce6-4328-a4c7-a7f300169dbd --><!-- begin field d780692a-7a06-499f-97f2-a7f300169dbd --><p>Any individual (or organization) involved in developing, reviewing, or commenting on clinical content, particularly the recommendations should declare competing interests. This includes the authoring team members, expert advisers, external reviewers of draft topics, individuals providing feedback on published topics, and Editorial Steering Group members. Declarations of interest are completed annually for authoring team and editorial steering group members, and are completed at the start of the topic update and development process for external stakeholders.</p><!-- end field d780692a-7a06-499f-97f2-a7f300169dbd --><!-- begin field 1b16188e-aa0d-44cc-ad5d-a7f300169dbd --><h2>Competing interests declared for this topic:</h2><!-- end field 1b16188e-aa0d-44cc-ad5d-a7f300169dbd --><!-- begin field 0bb43eea-8e85-403c-9500-a7f300169dbd --><p>None.</p><!-- end field 0bb43eea-8e85-403c-9500-a7f300169dbd --><!-- end item aa213e69-0226-4d0e-a9a5-a7f30015bd73 -->","topic":{"id":"be4f3502-607b-5fee-a51f-95c6bd0b5ec2","topicId":"3d44f060-93e8-484f-9435-bbf95181522e","topicName":"Herpes simplex - ocular","slug":"herpes-simplex-ocular","lastRevised":"Last revised in November 2016","chapters":[{"id":"32c3fcc5-456d-5b9d-aef9-f9b7c680badd","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"da713d91-bc3d-5555-b895-94dbfb914de7","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"80008612-da47-5830-afb3-976738b8bf37","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"b8f32462-8266-5dab-84a0-98008de3a98a","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"b5bcc37c-9baa-52ae-a626-8f354255e727","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"19396da1-78c6-52cf-a8fa-745a86678eb2","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"b60fab70-f81b-5b0d-9b5d-08bd0dc46221","slug":"goals","fullItemName":"Goals"},{"id":"3eb1fb97-b9d8-5e05-a603-311b22d98080","slug":"outcome-measures","fullItemName":"Outcome measures"},{"id":"0f62044c-c052-5413-8ef8-21290d58e558","slug":"audit-criteria","fullItemName":"Audit criteria"},{"id":"ddaf1eef-bf9a-50e0-abd6-040b5715c39f","slug":"qof-indicators","fullItemName":"QOF indicators"},{"id":"07f3c697-4a81-587b-8162-5ff58b04bea4","slug":"qipp-options-for-local-implementation","fullItemName":"QIPP - Options for local implementation"},{"id":"6c18f6c2-34ed-5878-8b6a-2be464339fb2","slug":"nice-quality-standards","fullItemName":"NICE Quality standards"}]},{"id":"c7601367-2c22-51ed-9e9c-69cb46ffed80","fullItemName":"Background information","slug":"background-information","subChapters":[{"id":"c75b7514-e5fb-592b-a2df-81eec31841ad","slug":"definition","fullItemName":"Definition"},{"id":"de6a22f7-5261-5085-88ae-5657084dce82","slug":"transmission","fullItemName":"Transmission"},{"id":"dd7dfd40-7c2d-5774-966b-96634e107bda","slug":"prevalence","fullItemName":"Prevalence"},{"id":"be0f06a6-bf75-59ac-9300-dedb534d3c57","slug":"complications","fullItemName":"Complications"},{"id":"4d4af1ea-a1a1-5e21-9573-d74d852e6047","slug":"prognosis","fullItemName":"Prognosis"}]},{"id":"213963cd-f53f-56f5-8b11-f11186a81308","fullItemName":"Diagnosis","slug":"diagnosis","subChapters":[{"id":"28841263-81bc-56fe-a67d-62350e0b0f8f","slug":"diagnosis","fullItemName":"Diagnosis"},{"id":"3605db60-be4b-5f87-9ca5-0a6c61f296b5